RACE.FOOTNOTES: LEAVEITONTHEFIELD sprinted out to the lead soon after the start and crossed over to the inside, led the way under some pressure from REVINER in the opening quarter then widened to a clear advantage, continued to pull away from the field up the backstretch, hustled along two wide around the far turn, drifted out wider, encouraged right handed, remained unchallenged and finished in hand. SKYLINE was off to a good start and raced two wide into the first turn, rated off the clear pacesetter up the backstretch, came under a ride around the far turn, swung three wide into the lane, was no match for pulling away winner but sustained bid and finished clearly second best. REVENIR raced in striking distance of LEAVEITONTHEFIELD in the opening quarter before rival pulled away from the field, chased the clear leader up the backstretch and around the far turn, came two wide into the stretch run and churned on for a share. GABRIEL'S LEGEND was unhurried and raced in the back around the first turn, continued reserved up the backstretch, saved ground around the far turn and failed to move into contention.

TOPPER T cleared the lead and crossed over soon after the start, continued to lead the way up the backstretch, took on the challenge of OUR LAST CHANCE at the five sixteenths pole, matched strides around the turn then got collared by the eventual winner heading into the lane and gave way.
